    FinishingOperation, Triplet, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class FinishingOperationImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements FinishingOperation
    An implementation of the model object 'Finishing Operation'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • FOp Type
    • Ref Edge
    • FOp Cnt
    • Ax Offst
    • Op Pos
